      <p class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">The Velveteen Ensemble will work with you to make your event a smashing success.  Our exclusive arranger and gifted musicians will ensure that the music played, performed, or recorded is of the utmost quality.  We have years of experience performing at the most acclaimed concert halls internationally, and have just returned from a five-week, twenty-concert series in <b>China</b>.</p>  
